<section>
<title>xboard</title>
<subtitle>Chess graphical interface</subtitle>
<para>
This software is a graphical interface to a chess engine, normally
gnuchess, or a fics server that permit to play via network with other
people or in tourney. It have a very intuitive interface and have a
lot of option. 
</para>
<para>
If you want play versus computer or versus a friend of yours just
type xboard. If you want to log on a Fics server type:
xboard -ics -icshost ficshostname
</para>
<para>
Freechess.org is a really good free Fics server where you can log.
</para>
</section>
